title: When is Tahm Kench coming out?
body: Hi every one I'm korean21support I just wanted to know when is Tahm Kench coming out? I'm very excited about him :)

replies.body: once things like champs are put up on the pbe they usually come out in the next patch so he should be out in the next patch, and the patches are usually 2 weeks apart so in about 9 days is my guess
Champion come out the day after league post a champion spotlight on youtube
well unless he's any different from every other champ to come out ever he will be available day of or day after patch
